simumatch.common

Enum Action

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Action>
      • simumatch.common.Action
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Action>

    public enum Action
extends java.lang.Enum<Action>
    An action that can be performed by a team in a match.

    This class is actually just an enumeration of all possible actions with their names. Effects of these Action s are represented by the Effect class, and should be loaded from files using an AbilitiesData object.
